Number = {{2}},
Month = {{MAR}},
Abstract = {{After more than one hundred years of development, the small hydropower
   (SHP) development rate of China has reached 58\% with limited potential
   for hydropower exploitation in many provinces. In addition to the
   challenges of safety, efficiency, and social benefit-sharing, the
   environmental impact has become a tough challenge for the development of
   SHP in China. Based on successful experiences with green hydropower
   certification internationally {[}Bratrich et al., River Res. Appl.
   20(7), 865-882 (2004); Low Impact Hydropower Certification Program (Low
